@startuml
title Threshold Event Detection

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> ReadPercent

ReadPercent : calculate selected interval
ReadPercent --> WaitingForSamples : percentage is NaN
WaitingForSamples --> ReadPercent : next collection

ReadPercent --> BelowThreshold : rounded percent < threshold
BelowThreshold --> ReadPercent : next collection

ReadPercent --> Cooldown : now < event floor
Cooldown --> ReadPercent : floor expired

ReadPercent --> EventRecorded : percent >= threshold\nand floor expired
EventRecorded : increment psistat_event_total
EventRecorded : store timestamp and percent
EventRecorded : set floor = now + interval
EventRecorded --> ReadPercent : next collection

@enduml
